---
title: Spicy Harissa and Apricot Chicken Tenders with Couscous, Tzatziki and Feta
description: This meal has a warming balance of sweet, spicy North African-inspired flavours. Fruity apricot and fiery harissa coat chicken tenders in a sticky sauce, while a dollop of creamy tzatziki to cool it all down.
